 * Hardware:
 *   - SoC: Qualcomm IPQ8072A (Quad-core Cortex-A53 @ 2.2GHz)
 *   - RAM: 512MB DDR3
 *   - Flash: W25R512NWEIQ 64MB SPI NOR (upgraded from 4MB)
 *   - Switch: QCA8075 (2x GbE LAN ports)
 *   - WLAN: QCN5024/QCN5054 (WiFi 6, ath11k)
 *   - 5G: Qualcomm SDX55 (X55) via PCIe
